# Takumi Guard (registry proxy for supply chain protection)
# See ADR-0002: docs/decisions/0002-introduce-takumi-guard-for-supply-chain-protection.md
#
# Setup:
#   1. Get a token at https://shisho.dev/ (email auth, free, no account needed)
#   2. cp .npmrc.example .npmrc
#   3. Replace tg_anon_REPLACE_ME with your token
#   4. NEVER commit .npmrc (.gitignore covers it)

registry=https://npm.flatt.tech/
//npm.flatt.tech/:_authToken=tg_anon_REPLACE_ME
